title: Welcome to Coffee with Kailey!
description: Welcome to the show, Coffee with Kailey! Each Wednesday, Kailey invites everyone to sit down and have coffee with her and her friends. As a touring wife and mother, Kailey gets to the heart of the matter with the people that matter most to her. She and her friends will catch up over a cup of coffee, sharing intimate stories of their lives. So, come share a cup and listen as they open up in this twelve episode podcast.
